data.description: Adorable Cape Cod style home located in the incredible town of Waldport. This well maintained 3Bed/3Bath home offers main level living. 2bed/2Bath on the main level &1Bed/1Bath, plus Loft/Office area on the second floor. Upstairs Bath w/Radiant Heated flooring/Epoxy countertop/Walk-in shower. Spacious finished basement is a fantastic additional living space/Bonus room and has a walk-in storage closet with built-in shelfing. It can be accessed from the main entry or garage. The large covered front porch is a peaceful place to sit back, unwind and take in the coastal air. With a large deck that runs the length of the house, Garden Beds, Greenhouse, Plum & Nectarine trees, the backyard offers an ideal space for entertaining and outdoor activities. Close to Golf/Crabbing/Fishing/State Parks.
